=== Pronunciation ===
[[Category:Hebrew language]]
ימן / yâman / yaw-man'
=== Etymology ===

A primitive root; 
=== Verb ===
to be (physically) right (that is, firm); but used only as denominative from  [[ימין]] {{HH|3225}} and transitively, to be right handed or take the right hand side: - go (turn) to (on, use) the right hand.
[[fr:ימן]]